#> 1         118         140.    NA    NA            NA
#> 2         118         132.     0     8.18         NA
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
anova(fit1, fit3, test = "LRT") # same anova(fit2, fit3)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
